Eliminate Service Outages




WATCH THE VIDEO

                    TRY THE DEMO
            


















Proactively Identify Service Issues, Pinpoint Disruptions, and Automate Remediation



Business service outages negatively impact customers, partners, and
  employees—resulting in financial losses and damage to company
  reputation. With ServiceNow, eliminate outages with a service‑aware
  approach, ingest operational information, and enable IT to proactively
  address issues and quickly respond to incidents.

















Proactively Identify Issues



Know the status of critical business services through a single
  dashboard. IT will be the first to know before problems arise.



                    VIEW DEMO
            




















Instantly see critical issues

Instantly see critical issues
Instantly see critical issues







                    VIEW DEMO
            

















Pinpoint Disruptions



Quickly identify the business services experiencing problems. Review
  the infrastructure and operational data to determine root cause and
  the best approach to resolution.



                    EXPLORE OUR SERVICE MAPPING PRODUCT
            




















Instantly review and rollback associated changes to mapped services

Instantly review and rollback associated changes to mapped services
Instantly review and rollback associated changes to mapped services





Diagnose and remediate issues

Diagnose and remediate issues
Diagnose and remediate issues





Instantly determine the severity of an alert

Instantly determine the severity of an alert
Instantly determine the severity of an alert







                    EXPLORE OUR SERVICE MAPPING PRODUCT
            

















Automate Remediation



Reduce time to resolution by seamlessly connecting information,
  people, and processes. Automatically remediate problems and initiate
  the incident process, understand the impact of change, gain approvals
  as needed, and continually communicate with all stakeholders through
  resolution on a single platform.



                    EXPLORE ORCHESTRATION
            




















Automate and accelerate remediation processes

Automate and accelerate remediation processes
Automate and accelerate remediation processes







                    EXPLORE ORCHESTRATION
            















How to Eliminate Service Outages

























1

											Map Business Services To Infrastructure
										




											Discover and map relationships between business services and the IT components required to support them.
										

Next >












2

											Keep Service Maps Current
										




											Continuously monitor IT infrastructure for changes and update service maps in real time.
										

< Prev
|
Next >












3

											Ingest Events From Across The IT Landscape
										




											Gain a consolidated view of service-impacting events for a rapid and effective IT response.
										

< Prev
|
Next >












4

											Prioritize Issues And Automate Fixes
										




											Automate IT and business processes to accelerate remediation, reduce manual tasks, and improve productivity.
										

< Prev
|
Next >












5

											Gain Visibility Into Business Service Health
										




											Prioritize the resolution of issues to ensure business service availability.
										

< Prev



























