ServiceNow Integrates With Your Existing Security Investments




















Minimize noise and prioritize alerts based on business impact, while
  also coordinating incident response workflows across teams and
  disparate security tools.



                    AVAILABLE IN SPLUNKBASE
            














Automated data enrichment and firewall rule updates can accelerate
  time to identify and time to remediate to reduce exposure to potential
  security risks.














Create and enrich security incidents from IBM QRadar SIEM.



                    AVAILABLE IN THE IBM X-FORCE EXCHANGE
            














Map vulnerabilities to configuration items and business services to
  determine impact and priority and drive remediation through a
  coordinated workflow.














Synchronize discovered assets and vulnerabilities for closed‑loop
  information as they are remediated.



                    AVAILABLE IN THE SERVICENOW STORE
            














Investigate a security incident by requesting endpoint process
  information from Tanium Endpoint Platform.














Import Tenable Security Center vulnerability data to build better
  workflows, reports and metrics for improved vulnerability visibility,
  context and action.



                    AVAILABLE IN THE SERVICENOW STORE
            














Create security incidents and search with McAfee Enterprise Security Manager.
















Isolate an endpoint or get a list of running processes associated
  with Cb Endpoint Security Platform.
















Integrate customized actionable threat intelligence with CrowdStrike
  Falcon Intelligence.
















Establish the prevalence of a threat and analyze data in real time
  with Elasticsearch.
















Create security incidents when bot infections are detected with Check
  Point Anti‑Bot.
















Search your data and create security incidents with HPE Security ArcSight.
















Look up indicators of compromise to validate potential threats with MetaDefender.
















Analyze suspicious files or URLs from security incidents with VirusTotal.
















Search for real time threat intelligence using security incident
  observables in Recorded Future.







































































